  Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§Ia5-sou chhut-si3 i2-cheng5 sou2 siu2--e5, chiu7-si7 taN e5 Le2-pai3-lak8, mia5-kio3 An-hioh-jit8; sou2-ki3--e5 si7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 thiN-te7, lang5, mih8 e5 toa7 kong-lo5. Ia5-sou koh-oah8 e5 liau2-au7, sou2 siu2--e5 si7 chai7-cha2 e5 Le2-pai3-jit8, chiu7-si7 chit-tiap8 e5 Le2-pai3-jit8, ia7 mia5-cho3 Chu2-jit8; sou2 ki3--e5 si7 Ia5-sou koh-oah8, kap seng5-chiu7 lang5 kiu3-se3 siok8-choe7 e5 toa7 kong-lo5. In-ui7 Siong7-te3 kiu3-se3 e5 kong-lo5, khah toa7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 e5 kong-lo5; sou2-i2 ke2-oaN7 hit jit8 lai5 siu2 i. 
  Ia5-sou e5 hak8-seng put-lun7 ti7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, na7 kau3 chit-chit8-jit8 eng-kai tioh8 an-hioh it-khai3 e5 se3-su7, tiam3 ke-lai7 khoaN3 chheh kong2 to7-li2 ki5-to2. Na7 u7 pai3-tng5 chiu7 kau3 pai3-tng5, kap cheng3-lang5 gim5-si, keng3-khian5 cho3-hoe2 ki5-to2, thiaN lang5 kong2 hok-im lai5 tiau7-iong2 sim-sin5; siat-lip8 thiN-teng2 hiong2-siu7 An-hioh eng2-oan2 e5 te7-ki.¡¨I-e5 bou2 koh mng7,¡§Le2-pai3-jit8 na7 cha-pou ia7 tioh8 theng5-kang; cha-bou2 ia7 m7-thang phang2-chit, cho3 khang-khoe3, se2 in-chiuN5 hiah-e5 su7, ke-su7 kiam2 bo5 khah khiam3-khoeh mah?¡¨Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§M7-sai2 hoan5-lo2 kau3 koe3-thau5, thiaN Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7 khah iau3-kin2. Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3 lan2 lak8 jit8, hou7 lan2 ke3-bou5 chiah8 chheng7, lai5 iuN2-chhi7 seng-khu ke-lai7; beng7-leng7 lan2 tioh8 chiong chit8 jit8 lai5 hok8-sai7 I, chiau3 i e5 beng7-leng7 lai5 kiaN5, kiam2 m7-si7 eng-kai e5 cheng5-li2 mah? Na7 chhiat sim kiu5 Siong7-te3 e5 kok kap jin5-gi7, sou2 eng7 e5 mih8 Siong7-te3 tek-khak siuN2-su3--lan2. Iu7-koh cho3 seng-li2 than3-chiN5, put-ko3 si7 in-ui7 iuN2-chhi7 hek8-sin nia7-nia7, na7 le2-pai3 ku2 si7 iuN2-chhi7 leng5-hun5; than3-chiN5 che si7 kan-ta ui7-tioh8 chiam7-si5 se3-kan e5 hok, le2-pai3 ku2 si7 ui7-tioh8 eng2-oan2 Thian-tong5 e5 hok. Nng7 hang7 lai5 pi2, sim2-mih8 khah tang7, sim2-mih8 khah khin, tioh8 chai thang keng2. 
