  Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§Beng5-pek8 to7-li2, tiau5-kou3-i3 lai5 kiaN5 ho2, khiok ho2 leh. Na7-si7 ti7 chit-e5 to7-li2 e5 tiong-kan, iau2-ku2 u7 khah chin3-pou7 leh. Siat-su2 m7-si7 chhiong-moa2 ti7 Seng3-sin5-e5, be7 chin3-pou7; kau3 chin3-pou7 chiu7 e7 an-jian5 chu7-chai7 lai5 kiaN5, chu7-jian5 hap8 to7-li2. TaN goa2 ka-ti7 sit8-chai7 bo5 pian3-hoa3 goa2 sim e5 chai5-leng5, iah8 bo5 pian3-hoa3 pat8-lang5 e5 sim e5 khui3-lat8. Che si7 Seng3-sin5 e5 koan5-leng5, Siong7-te3 chi3-toa7 e5 in-tian2 sou2 siuN2-su3; sou2-i2 kiu5 chiu7 tek-khak tit-tioh8; bo5 kiu5, chiu7 be7 tit-tioh8. 
