  Hian5-chhe iu7 koh kong2, su-iok8 oh-tit se2 chheng. Keng--nih8 iah8 u7 kong2, ¡§Siong7-te3 bat kong2,¡¥Goa2 eng7 chheng e5 chui2 ka7 li2 se2, hou7 li2 e7 chheng-khi3; hoan7-na7 u3-oe3 e5 tai7-chi3 long2 se2-tu5 kau3 chheng-khi3.¡¦Sou2-i2 chai7-cha2 Tai7-pit8 ong5 kiu5 Chu2 kong2,¡¥Chu2 na7 hou7 goa2 chheng-khi3, goa2 chiu7 chheng-khi3, Chu2 na7 se2-thoa7--goa2, goa2 chiu7 pi2 seh khah peh8.¡¦Goa2 goan7 hian5-chhe oh8 Tai7-pit8 ong5 seng5-sim khun2-kiu5, bo5 loa7-ku2 chiu7 u7 eng3-giam7.¡¨ 
